query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from so_user AS u1
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'diy',
'ell',
'scifi',
'webmasters')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('bathroom',
'doctor-who',
'domains',
'homework',
'idioms',
'phrase-usage',
'repair',
'switch')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Constituent',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Fanatic',
'Guru',
'Peer Pressure',
'Pundit',
'Quorum',
'Suffrage',
'Tag Editor',
'Tumbleweed') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
